import CompanyCard from "../../components/ui/CompanyCard/CompanyCard";
import { card, cards as cards } from "./cards";
import { Container, Title, Wrap } from "./styled";

export default function Home() {
  const cards: card[] = cards;
  
  return (
    <Wrap>
      <Title>Каталог компаний</Title>
      <Container>
        <CompanyCard
          imgUrl="https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000635780677-yhmbpw-t500x500.jpg"
          title="Для авто"
        />
        <CompanyCard
          imgUrl="https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000635780677-yhmbpw-t500x500.jpg"
          title="Здоровье"
        />
        <CompanyCard
          imgUrl="https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000635780677-yhmbpw-t500x500.jpg"
          title="Развлечения"
        />
        <CompanyCard
          imgUrl="https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000635780677-yhmbpw-t500x500.jpg"
          title="Бьюти"
        />
        <CompanyCard
          imgUrl="https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000635780677-yhmbpw-t500x500.jpg"
          title="Ремонт"
        />
        <CompanyCard
          imgUrl="https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000635780677-yhmbpw-t500x500.jpg"
          title="Услуги"
        />
      </Container>
    </Wrap>
  );
}
